On 4 Jul 2020 (as of midnight 4 Jul 2020):
- 8 new cases of confirmed infections (6 imported cases, 3 in Gansu province, 1 in Tianjin municipality, 1 in Shanghai municipality and 1 in Sichuan province; 2 indigenous cases, both in Beijing municipality), 1 new case of suspected infections (an imported case in Shanghai), and no deaths.
- A total of 1931 imported cases have been reported.
- 83 553 confirmed cases and 4634 deaths; 78 516 recovered and discharged from hospital; 763 557 close contacts with infected patients, and 4993 are under medical observation.
